Manual install :
 - create folder /var/lib/pulse2/imaging, export it throught NFS (async, rw, subtree_check)
 - create folder /var/lib/pulse2/imaging/log/
 - create folder /var/lib/pulse2/imaging/images/
 - create folder /var/lib/pulse2/imaging/etc/
 - create folder /usr/share/pulse2/imaging
 - install src/pulse2-imaging-server under /usr/sbin/
 - install init.d/pulse2-imaging-server under /etc/init.d/
 - install contrib/skel into /usr/share/pulse2/imaging/skel
 - install conf/pulse2/imaging-server/imaging-server.ini under /etc/mmc/conf/pulse2/imaging-server/
 - install helpers into /usr/share/pulse2/imaging
